N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6211.5 - Privacy of Voting

State Regulations

To ensure an efficient and fair early voting process that
respects the privacy of the voter, the manner of voting on days of the early
voting period shall be the same as the manner of voting on the day of
election. Notes
